Setup sudoers. Add the operating system user name to sudoers.

{{Box|text=
Become root.

{{CodeSelect|code=
su
}}

Add the {{Code2|user}} account to the sudoer's group. Replace {{Code2|user}} with the actual operating system user name.

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo adduser user sudo
}}

Reboot so group changes take effect.

{{CodeSelect|code=
reboot
}}
